## What's Next

Day 54 begins the Implement step — the fourth step of the NIST RMF. Implementation is where the SSP's documented controls are translated into actual system configuration, deployed procedures, and operational reality. For OpenMRS, some implementation is already complete. The Implement step also addresses the security configuration documentation and baseline capture that provides the assessment team's reference point.

